Content Context:
- Cyber Kill Chain (Lockheed Martin): 7 stages - Reconnaissance (passive/active info gathering, e.g., DNS queries), Weaponization (exploit/malware assembly), Delivery (phishing/email), Exploitation (code execution), Installation (backdoor/DLL), C2 (beaconing), Actions on Objectives (data exfil/lateral movement).
